{"type":"question","id":18611,"title":"站在今天如何看待2018年火极一时的《中共高官谈时局》？","uid":9686,"topics":[5262,136,1,161,367],"contents":"转自 老灯<br>\n中共高官谈时局<br>\n<blockquote>这篇中共高官谈时局，是我2018年初电邮采访国内朋友的文字记录，陆续公开发表在推特上，有推友汇总整理后发给我。现在重新贴出，仅供大家参考。<br>\n我想告诉各位朋友的是，中共高层绝非铁板一块，内部的争斗倾轧异常激烈，各种故意放话出口转内销，错综复杂奥妙无穷，我们看戏便好，嘿嘿</blockquote><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/laodeng89/status/1228935362627563520\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/laodeng89/status/1228935362627563520</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EQ4OL8GUEAAUKZR?format=jpg&amp;name=4096x4096\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EQ4OL8GUEAAUKZR?format=jpg&amp;name=4096x4096\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EQ4OL8GUEAAUKZR?format=jpg&amp;name=4096x4096\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EQ4OL8GU0AADrJT?format=jpg&amp;name=4096x4096\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EQ4OL8GU0AADrJT?format=jpg&amp;name=4096x4096\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EQ4OL8GU0AADrJT?format=jpg&amp;name=4096x4096\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EQ4OL8IU4AAHQaI?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EQ4OL8IU4AAHQaI?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EQ4OL8IU4AAHQaI?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EQ4OL8PVUAAh27Y?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EQ4OL8PVUAAh27Y?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EQ4OL8PVUAAh27Y?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<blockquote>曾经轰动海内外的另一篇高官谈时局<br>\n陆续发布于2018年7月<br>\n时过境迁<br>\n重读此文感慨不已<br>\n如果当时高层换马成功<br>\n现在的中国必是另一番景象<br>\n何至于天灾人祸不断<br>\n看来一切均为天命也……</blockquote><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EQ4oroYU0AAwiJv?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EQ4oroYU0AAwiJv?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EQ4oroYU0AAwiJv?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-02-16","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":2}